{"tid":1738934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[work?]理撚得佢藍定黃，無貼文宣就唔幫襯","createTime":"2019-11-19T11:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T12:01:52.000Z","uid":27754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7ae6d3bf4759284ee770b71942168031a452e190","tid":1738934,"uid":27754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:48:04.000Z","msg":"就無國界醫生都跪一事，我諗緊唔知呢條橋work唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其我地日日痴文宣比人搣，我地可否整文宣派比鋪頭商户，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">由我地本身重點懲罰黃店，變成標籤非黃店既鋪頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>理撚得佢藍定黃，無貼文宣就唔幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n就好似之前搞個d有營食肆，正品正貨商戶，caring company 咁<br />\n<br />\n實際做法係先用文宣FB, IG，TG煲幾日，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"></span></span>舉例由12月1號開始，市民不再幫襯無文宣既鋪頭，<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">當生意額下降，唔夠隔離爭，佢地就會驚，好似依家個個都想認證做黄店咁</span></span></strong></span>，當直至佢地有第一張文宣開始，文宣組就可以行動不斷供新野比佢地<br />\n<br />\n咁樣鋪頭為左<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">加入黃色經濟圈</span></strong></span>，就算藍既都會跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其次本身消費者，食客都會好似睇得CCTVB多咁，潛移默化加入我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，再者又可以恢復返市場既平衡，唔洗李嘉誠拎光環，藍絲食環又唔敢隨便撕私人地方既野，大家話work唔work?<br />\n<br />\n如果有連鎖集團加入做呢件事，個影響力應該會仲大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">讓文宣組一齊加入經濟戰！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4d18b428c5da838298f5698d4c1c6a69526d3c04","tid":1738934,"uid":27754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d734cd6f26981ac7f9a5f71019e11c956fdea829","tid":1738934,"uid":324266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"其實講得好岩 d惡勢力無錢搵就自然收皮 點解大都唔否以忍忍口?  雖然煩d但深黃商店都好好食 再唔係我味自己煮囉當儲錢"},{"pid":"526dfbd00d6ff704ae9e1e8c00154b2c2c1959be","tid":1738934,"uid":27754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}